<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Chinese Defense Minister Back in Urumqi </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
URUMQI, Xingjiang, June 20 (Xinhua) -- Chi Haotian,
vice-chairman of the Central Military Commission, state
councillor and defense minister, returned here at the end of an
official goodwill visit to Belarus, Ukraine, Kazakhstan and
Kirghizstan.
</P>
<P>
On his way home via Alma-Ata, capital of Kazakhstan, Kazakh
Defense Minister Mukhtar Kapashevich Altynbayev was among those
who greeted and saw Chi and his party off at the airport. 
</P>
