</P>
<P>
U.S. officials here say that Clinton will try to gain support
from other G-7 countries to help Moscow to join the international
institutions.
</P>
<P>
"We're making progress with Russia, but it has not yet
formulated its market access offers," U.S. Trade Representative
Charlene Barshefsky told reporters when referring to Russia's
joining in WTO.
</P>
<P>
"Ideally, we would like Russia to be able to move quickly, but
the substance is not there yet," she added. 
