Raoux will meet in the other semi-final match.
</P>
<P>
In the women's competitions, top seed Anke Huber of Germany and
Miriam Oremans of the Netherlands saw their close semi-final
battle halted by rain after each winning a set.
</P>
<P>
The decisive set will be played on Saturday and the winner will
go on to meet third seed Ruxandra Dragomir of Romania in the final
later on Saturday. 
